  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/System\/Errno\/connectionAbort\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:03:23Z\n---\n\n# connectionAbort\n\n**Type Property**\n\nSoftware caused a connection abort.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var connectionAbort: Errno { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nA connection abort was caused internal to your host machine.\n\nThe corresponding C error is `ECONNABORTED`.\n\n## Network Errors\n\n- **connectionRefused**: Connection refused.\n- **connectionReset**: Connection reset by peer.\n- **hostIsDown**: The host is down.\n- **messageTooLong**: Message too long.\n- **networkDown**: Network is down.\n- **networkReset**: Network dropped connection on reset.\n- **networkUnreachable**: Network is unreachable.\n- **noBufferSpace**: No buffer space available.\n- **noRouteToHost**: No route to host.\n- **notSupported**: Not supported.\n- **timedOut**: Operation timed out.\n\n",
